  <brief_title>A Phase Ⅱ Study of an All-Oral Combination of Low-dose Etoposide/Capecitabine in Patients With Metastatic Breast Cancer Previously Treated With Anthracyclines and/or Taxanes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase Ⅱ Study of an All-Oral Combination of Low-dose Etoposide/Capecitabine in Patients With Metastatic Breast Cancer Previously Treated With Anthracyclines and/or Taxanes</official_title>
