  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single-center, open-lable, non-comparative, prospective, phase Ⅱ efficacy and
      safety study. Eligible patients are enrolled in a single group. The investigators propose to
      determine the efficacy and safety of low-dose metronomic chemotherapy with
      Etoposide/Capecitabine in Patients with Metastatic Breast Cancer Previously Treated with
      Anthracyclines and/or Taxanes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
